description: The Skinomi MatteSkin Full Body Skin Protector is a revolutionary new way to protect your device. Perfect for outdoor use, MatteSkin Protectors provide a great solution to increase visibility of your mobile device when used outdoors or bright environments.

Custom-designed and laser-fit for maximum coverage, the MatteSkin Protector provides a unique layer of protective coating made to give your device a smooth, lasting finish. Additionally, a special UV-resistant coating prevents yellowing and is engineered to minimize fingerprints to offer a perfect, full-body solution for safeguarding all your mobile devices.

As with all Skinomi products, we're so confident that you'll love the Skinomi MatteSkin that every screen protector and full body skin protector is covered with a Lifetime Warranty. If the Skinomi MatteSkin wears off, gets scratched, or damaged in any way, we'll replace it.
